@startuml zeropaper_visual-fiha

[VFExtension] as "VFExtension\n(Core Orchestrator)"
[WebServer] as "WebServer"
[DisplayWorker] as "DisplayWorker"
[Layers] as "Layers"
[ScriptRunner] as "ScriptRunner"
[Scriptable] as "Scriptable"
[Redux Store] as "Redux Store"
[Webviews] as "Webviews"
[Capture] as "Capture"
[Com] as "Com"
[Commands] as "Commands"

VFExtension --> WebServer : manages
VFExtension --> Redux Store : uses
VFExtension --> Webviews : manages
VFExtension --> Commands : exposes

WebServer --> DisplayWorker : serves
WebServer --> Capture : serves

DisplayWorker --> Layers : renders
DisplayWorker --> ScriptRunner : uses

Layers --> Scriptable : uses

Redux Store --> Com : updates via

Webviews --> Redux Store : reads/updates
Webviews --> Com : communicates via

Capture --> Com : sends data via

Com --> VFExtension : facilitates communication

Commands --> VFExtension : executed by

@enduml